Philip Ahn https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Philip_Ahn 0 Philip Ahn (born Pil Lip Ahn (안필립), March 29, 1905 – February 28, 1978) was a Korean American actor. He was the first Korean American film actor to receive a star on the Hollywood Walk of Fame.
